languages.text: В корабельной крипте покоятся представители династии фон Валанциус и их вернейшие подданные, что были удостоены чести сопровождать Вольных Торговцев после смерти.

languages.text: En la cripta de la nave descansan los miembros de la casa von Valancius y los súbditos leales que recibieron el honor de acompañar a sus Comerciantes Independientes más allá de la muerte.
languages.original_text: Laid to rest in the ship's crypt are members of House von Valancius and their loyal subjects who were given the honour of accompanying their Rogue Traders beyond the grave.

languages.text: 船の地下墓地に眠っているのは、フォン・ヴァランシウス家の一族とその忠実な臣下たちだ。彼らは自由開拓者より、墓の向こうまで同行する栄誉を与えられている。
languages.original_text: Laid to rest in the ship's crypt are members of House von Valancius and their loyal subjects who were given the honour of accompanying their Rogue Traders beyond the grave.

languages.text: 冯·瓦兰修斯家族的众多成员与忠诚的臣民在旗舰上的地下墓穴中安息。这些忠诚的臣民被授予了无上殊荣，即便是死后也能陪伴在行商浪人身边。
languages.original_text: Laid to rest in the ship's crypt are members of House von Valancius and their loyal subjects who were given the honour of accompanying their Rogue Traders beyond the grave.

languages.text: In der Krypta des Schiffes ruhen die verstorbenen Mitglieder des Hauses derer von Valancius und ihre treuen Untertanen, denen die Ehre zuteil wurde, ihre Freihändler über den Tod hinaus zu begleiten.
languages.original_text: Laid to rest in the ship's crypt are members of House von Valancius and their loyal subjects who were given the honour of accompanying their Rogue Traders beyond the grave.

languages.text: Dans la crypte du vaisseau reposent les membres de la maison von Valancius et leurs loyaux sujets qui ont reçu l'insigne honneur d'accompagner leurs libres-marchands dans la mort.
